Body: Description: The customer is on NEA version 11.6.0.74 and wants to upgrade to the latest version due to a SQL issue.

What We've Learned Updated: The client is experiencing an issue with some SQL database servers. While running a report on some SQL servers, the client noticed some information was missing.
Since the report has no errors and the client is not using the latest version, I will upgrade the client to the newest version.
Next Steps Updated: Upgrade NEA to the latest version
